---

## ğŸ—ï¸ TECHNOLOGY STACK

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 15 + React 18 | Full-stack, fast, TypeScript support |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Type safety, fewer runtime errors |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL (Supabase) | Powerful, secure, RLS built-in |
| **Auth** | Supabase Auth | JWT-based, OAuth-ready |
| **Storage** | Supabase Storage | S3-backed, RLS protection |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first, zero custom CSS |
| **Hosting** | Vercel | Auto-scaling, free tier, HTTPS |
| **Validation** | Zod | Runtime schema validation |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form | Lightweight, performant |
| **State** | Zustand | Simple state management |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Beautiful, consistent icons |

**Total Lines of Dependencies:** ~50 packages  
**Bundle Size:** < 400KB (gzipped)  
**Build Time:** < 30 seconds  

