## ğŸ†˜ TROUBLESHOOTING

### Build Fails on Vercel
â†’ Check build logs. Usually missing env variable.

### Login Not Working
â†’ Verify Supabase credentials in `.env.local`

### Photos Not Uploading
â†’ Check storage bucket and RLS policies

### Dashboard Shows 404
â†’ Verify middleware.ts route protection

### Slow Performance
â†’ Run `npm run build` and check bundle size

**Full troubleshooting guide in Deployment Checklist**

